        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我能问问原理吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她眼中的好奇神色更浓了。我隐约听过，姬辰星在来到零区之前，是一位在脑神经学领域有所建树的前沿学者，她对“歌唱者”抱有学者的好奇。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抱歉，我也不是很清楚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "姬辰星仅仅是点了点头，没有继续询问。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当我们继续向那些树状结晶前进时，在深水区内看见了其余降临团的朝觐者，还有更多异化人。",
        "disable": 0
